### **Q14: Write JavaScript code to change the background color of the web page to red if the button named "RED" is clicked and to green if the button named "GREEN" is clicked.**

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Change Background Color</title>
</head>
<body>

  <button onclick="document.body.style.backgroundColor = 'red'">RED</button>
  <button onclick="document.body.style.backgroundColor = 'green'">GREEN</button>

</body>
</html>
```

